ext-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Barolo DOCG</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Piemont</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Król win i wino królów. Nebbiolo 100%.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase\"><span>W02</span><span class=\"border border-stone-700 px-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm\">RED</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Amarone della Valpolicella</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Veneto</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Metoda appassimento. Suszone winogrona.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase\"><span>W03</span><span class=\"border border-stone-700 px-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm\">RED</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Chianti Classico</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Toskania</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Serce Toskanii. Sangiovese min. 80%.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase\"><span>W04</span><span class=\"border border-stone-700 px-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm\">RED</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Brunello di Montalcino</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Toskania</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Długie starzenie. Sangiovese Grosso.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase\"><span>W05</span><span class=\"border border-stone-700 px-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm\">WHITE</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Etna Bianco</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Sycylia</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Wulkaniczne gleby. Carricante.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase\"><span>W06</span><span class=\"border border-stone-700 px-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm\">SPARKLING</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-stone-300 mb-1 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors\">Franciacorta</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Lombardia</p><p class=\"font-sans text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">Metoda klasyczna. Włoski szampan.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 border border-stone-800/60 bg-stone-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-none transition-colors group \"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2 opacity-50 font-mon